==English==
===Etymology===
Named after their usu. black plumage. Possibly also because they are [[brood]] [[parasite]]s.
===Noun===
{{en-noun2|'''widow bird'''|'''widow birds'''}}
#Any of several species of birds in the family [[Viduidae]], incorporating [[whydahs]] and [[widowfinch]]es.
